{"hash":"958d23982b9485558ae37fd7e5403920e8f6f2fd","data":{"post":{"id":"f7e21c0c9264a1875ffaa12fb39e4be7","title":"Introducing arjunanimations","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>I've started a new project, a suite of JS and CSS animations called ArjunAnimations. </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I feel like a lot of things happen just because my cousin yells at me to do it. </p>\n<h2 id=\"ideation\"><a href=\"#ideation\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Ideation</h2>\n<p>I've had these floating leaves on my website for nearly 2 years. At first they were hacked from another website, then I rebuilt them using GSAP. </p>\n<p>View on <a href=\"github.com/arjunkalburgi/arjunanimation_leaves\">GitHub</a>.\nView on <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@arjunanimations/leaves\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">NPM</a>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 600 300' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-4efeb9242917007a3a8e103369924e0c'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-4efeb9242917007a3a8e103369924e0c)' width='600' height='300' xlink:href='data:image/gif%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAgCAYAAACinX6EAAAACXBIWXMAAAPoAAAD6AG1e1JrAAAGK0lEQVRo3rVZaZObRhDl//%2bffElVUqlKKvmQy157vfLeWmm1ugUCAdIA7X4NAwNCAknI5SlxzDQzfbx%2b3WslUUJdD%2bKhooi2SlEUxXJ/qoyY111jb6nsQr7VreBUKA4/CW2633zQbOvIfd2hcK9HVQZFdBUlxGIQygYrIFa8gQ4HhAZqR8NgQQ%2bsgCkrIFBbeW7O054i3qESYz2Rv9vSInRTJXS%2bP6Ll1pX97dhDreu4WMyWX9OrP%2bWPeeJyhdZJ5iA0QlbULFzzRqLc4lDImL3naTOR9%2bnzDvcXJ/T3%2bol%2bs7/RghVhXcvF4AVzVoK%2bh1Wf/Ak5243cAx9eWEE97516m1F%2bWCjmzZ/THT93d0HuBV3FPn5h/X9YCaKArl1Mu3P%2b0cztet6Ifll9pc9uX1wQz97DJf28uqGflv/LwZNsLjzgOytFqSiX0dn%2bMm/0WLkBG8XqBvXp%2bHs%2b1zR06Iv3Rn8593I4WGO129Cv9i39bvf2gBDx2ST30j3ToSwgyKziViiMeVtx3